{"tid":1914371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇人會跳/跟 閘？","createTime":"2020-03-07T13:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T13:38:07.000Z","uid":95102,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e19c679fb23bb9a0a7c5f9aadc7f2da5506b1abc","tid":1914371,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"每次搭黨鐵一見到有人拍卡入閘都把鬼火，見今日有個捉閘鬼俾人打順便做個統計先<br />\n<br />\n<strong>跳閘 </strong><br />\n優點：型囉 <br />\n            唔使俾錢黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺點：太大動作會引起不必要嘅注要<br />\n            有可能俾人捉<br />\n            有體力需求<br />\n<br />\n<strong>跟閘</strong><br />\n優點：低調 <br />\n            唔使俾錢黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺點：有可能俾人捉（低機率）<br />\n            某部分站跟唔到<br />\n<br />\n<strong>拍卡</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母呀 仲俾錢黨鐵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>拍綠卡</strong><br />\n個人認為既然拍綠卡都會畀人捉 咁點解仲要畀錢佢？ 兩蚊都係錢呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我平時就跟開閘（利申一次都冇俾人捉過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）你哋平時係點？"},{"pid":"95a72c9206694af3894921af99287b20a0e17076","tid":1914371,"uid":95102,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:10:08.000Z","msg":"投票：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跳閘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟閘"},{"pid":"d53fda42092a278234a5dd53b789ae76b0a09745","tid":1914371,"uid":46309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"九月頭跳到家陣仲跳緊"},{"pid":"a529830df3e4f12bb8de711e9b35f55992f548f1","tid":1914371,"uid":95102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d53fda42092a278234a5dd53b789ae76b0a09745","tid":1914371,"uid":46309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"九月頭跳到家陣仲跳緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc01ef2481c64eb52a9296a5ae6f87d39595e59","tid":1914371,"uid":33899,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"直接唔搭，近半年搭唔多過3次"},{"pid":"cba4190db1b22868b997f2e133fba40eeef25b16","tid":1914371,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"跟同跳都有"},{"pid":"b5011b753aa86e600bfb2ede0bd4139958404f91","tid":1914371,"uid":57322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"今日見到有絲打跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望佢出閘都平安"},{"pid":"02bcfd34671b7772ef26bec5e1d808d9eac3172c","tid":1914371,"uid":341040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:13:58.000Z","msg":"爆閘<br />\n<br />\n大力小小推就得<br />\n<br />\n返工同埋屋企個站都係舊式閘<br />\n<br />\n好易推，又低調"},{"pid":"e22976c60588318ae9f8550afcc7ab1e2ba5af01","tid":1914371,"uid":95102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5011b753aa86e600bfb2ede0bd4139958404f91","tid":1914371,"uid":57322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"今日見到有絲打跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望佢出閘都平安"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"但係明明我次次入都見唔到有人跳/跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d2f7701cb6642f0f815172f885831b3ff69633","tid":1914371,"uid":185373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"唔比錢係咩心態<br />\n係咪即係去藍店食野 食完唔比錢走？"},{"pid":"a98c106c1d4b926181aeaa1fd1384ecb669e3b97","tid":1914371,"uid":243978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"其實點解要冒險被捉？<br />\n你兩樣也有機會被罰既<br />\n如果你要咁樣二選一既話<br />\n不如唔好去坐仲好啦 <br />\n唔想再看到有人被捉呀<br />\n人地職員係咩顏色<br />\n你從今日一事還沒看清嗎？<br />\n日後或者可能更加落力去捉"},{"pid":"7ac96f646cccdbd88cb26f